safetyTips: We comply by current food safety standards in our kitchen and our staff wear PPE and socially distance in the workplace. For contact-free delivery, we place orders on the doorstep and call the customer to collect from there.
name: Dulwich Lyceum
description: We offer a dine-at-home service for customers in the local area. Our ordering line is open every day 12-3pm and we deliver between 4-7pm. We offer small plates, salads, large dishes, desserts, wines, beers, and cocktails. We offer contact-free delivery, no minimum spend.
